1 McClatchy Co. Senior Product Manager Salaries 

Browse McClatchy Co. Salaries by Job Title →

McClatchy Co. Senior Product Managers earn $110,000 annually, or $53 per hour, which is equal to the national average for all Senior Product Managers at $110,000 annually and 57% higher than the national salary average for ​all working Americans. The highest paid Senior Product Managers work for Morgan Stanley at $163,000 annually and the lowest paid Senior Product Managers work for Conexant Systems at $56,000 annually.






