            McClatchy Interactive is a publishing system. It has launched electronic news sites on the Web, such as the Nando Times and the SportServer. The company was founded in 1857. It went public in 1988 and its newspapers also provide online publishing tools for media businesses and organizations across the United States and Canada. Its digital workbench is a content management and also offers editing solutions. The company s InSite product is an online registration system that is designed to collect demographic information about its readers. It offers various news, such as weather forecasts, lottery, horoscopes, movie listings, stock and business news. McClatchy Interactive additionally offers national and international news 24 hours a day. It is located in Raleigh, N.C.
          






















